message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_FV_INSRETTYPE_EMPTY
message.locale: The insurance return type must not be blank.

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_FV_TOTCONTRIBAMT_EMPTY
message.locale: The total contribution amount must be specified.

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_FV_TOTEMPLOYEES_EMPTY
message.locale: The total number of employees must be specified.

message.name: ERR_INSRETURNHEADER_XFV_RECEIPTDATE_LATE
message.locale: The receipt date cannot be later than today's date.

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_XFV_TOTCONTRIBAMT_EMPLOYEE_EMPLOYER
message.locale: The total contribution must be equal to the sum of the employee and employer contribution amounts.

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_XFV_TOTCONTRIBAMTPAYROLL
message.locale: Total contribution amount cannot exceed total payroll.

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_XFV_TOTNUMEMPLOYEES_PERMANENT_CASUAL
message.locale: The total number of employees must be equal to the number of permanent employees plus the number of casual employees.

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_XFV_TOTCONTRIBAMT_ZERO
message.locale: Total employer contribution amount or total employee contribution amount must be specified.

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_XFV_TOTNUMEMPLOYEES_ZERO
message.locale: Number of permanent employees or number of casual employees must be specified.

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_FV_TOTALEMPLOYERCONTRIBUTIONAMOUNTNEG
message.locale: Total employer contribution cannot be negative

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_FV_TOTALEMPLOYEECONTRIBUTIONAMOUNTNEG
message.locale: Total employee contribution cannot be negative

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_FV_TOTALNUMEMPLOYEES_CASUAL_NEGATIVE
message.locale: Number of casual employees cannot be negative

message.name: ERR_INSRETHEADER_FV_TOTALNUMEMPLOYEES_PERMANENT_NEGATIVE
message.locale: Number of permanent employees cannot be negative
